task.summary: working on making packet handling extensible -> created package api.packet.ext containing PacketManager and PacketFactory -> PacketManager will register all factories and be able to transform a byte sequence to a Packet from their registered Factories and vice-versa. -> PacketFactory contains the logic to transform a Packet to a byte sequence and vice-versa. -> removed Protocol.scala -> moved DataPacket and TaskInitPacket to packet.ext.fundamental

Starting CloudStorage extension ~> It will be 3 month since i started this project, i first wanted to create a simple private cloud storage system, with folder synchronization. But with the time, i wanted to make something more useful and powered. so i created a extensible program, and here is the result ! This extension will be the first extension that i could use every time with my personal computers.
-> Moved Tasks and Commands about File/Folder Downloading and Uploading from FundamentalExtension and ControllerExtension to CloudStorageExtension
-> Removed very bad handed made Folder Listeners, and reused WatchServices.
refactor some relayExtensionInfo to be in accordance with scala conventions
v0.1.1 Added Version apply method, Refactor api.RelayProperties to api.extension
Refactor project package root from vps.ftp to linkkit
